# More info: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file
# Ignore everything by default and re-include only needed files
**

# Re-include Go source files (but not *_test.go)
!**/*.go
**/*_test.go

# Re-include Go module files
!go.mod
!go.sum

# Re-include files embedded via //go:embed directives in the Go source.
# Both variants are included so the same build context can produce either
# the default ("latest") binary or the `-tags=dev` binary.
!config/images/defaults.latest.env
!config/images/defaults.dev.env

# Re-include pre-built binary (used by local Dockerfile)
!bin/manager
